---
title: Za'atar Pita Burgers with Zucchini Fries and Dill Tzatziki
description: Za’atar, a Middle Eastern spice blend composed of sumac,
sesame, thyme, and a variety of other dried herbs, infuses
these burgers with a unique, almost woodsy aroma. A mixture
of yogurt, dill, lemon, and cucumber makes for a bright, tangy
tzatziki sauce. It’s the perfect condiment for crispy oven-baked
zucchini fries.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/zaatar-pita-burgers-8b4567.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.ca/recipecards/card/zaatar-pita-burgers-8b4567.pdf
